name: Sporty Luxe Dress - Grey Jersey and Sequin
description:
A gorgeous grey marle jersey and sequin dress combination suitable for day or evenings! Featuring a relaxed fitting jersey top and a slightly more fitted sequin dress. The sequin part of the dress is lined, and has a gold zip at centre back. Grey marle with a pale gold sequin (Also available in a black and white stripe with a pale gold sequin).
Please note- this garment is designed to be fitted in the lower body, and has stretch. The measurements below are the relaxed garment measurements. Models are a size 8 wearing a size 8 dress.
